               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I went to Ruislip fair—it came on to rain—I stopped under a hovel—a man came there and stopped till daylight—he asked me if I wanted to buy a pair of shoes, he wanted 5<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. for them—I said I had but 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.—I put them on—they fitted me very well—I gave him the 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.</p>
